# ... rest of your code`} /></pre>
				<p>Restart the server with <code>uv run uvicorn main:app --reload</code>.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Try It Out</h2>
				<p>
					Open <code>index.html</code> in your browser. You'll see all your products!
					Use the search box to filter, and click "Buy" to simulate a purchase.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Congratulations!</h2>
				<p>
					You've built a complete stack‚ÄîPython backend API with a database, and a simple frontend UI.
					From here, you can add features like user accounts, real payment processing, image uploads, and more.
				</p>
				<p>
					Keep coding and building amazing things! üéâ
				</p>
			</section>
		</article>

		<div class="tutorial-nav">
			<a href="/tutorials/javascript" class="prev-btn">‚Üê Previous</a>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

